dfischer.proxysniffer

Class ProxyDataRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.proxysniffer.ProxyDataRecord

  • public class ProxyDataRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains one item of a recorded session. Such an item is either an URL call or a Page Break.
    See Also:
    getDataType(), getHttpRequest(), getHttpResponse(), getWebSocketData(), writeObject(java.io.DataOutputStream), readObject(java.io.DataInputStream), ProxyDataDump

      • ProxyDataRecord

        public ProxyDataRecord()

      • ProxyDataRecord

        public ProxyDataRecord(int recorderSequenceID,
               HttpPageBreak httpPageBreak)
        Standard constructor for page breaks.
        Parameters:
        recorderSequenceID - the recorder sequence ID (increased each time when reset/clear session of the proxy recorder is called). Pass a value of -1 (minus one) if the session is not recorded by the proxy recorder. Note that the sequence ID is reset when the recorder process is restarted.
        httpPageBreak - the page break data

      • ProxyDataRecord

        public ProxyDataRecord(int recorderSequenceID,
               HttpRequest httpRequest)
        Standard constructor for URLs.
        Parameters:
        recorderSequenceID - the recorder sequence ID (increased each time when reset/clear session of the proxy recorder is called). Pass a value of -1 (minus one) if the session is not recorded by the proxy recorder. Note that the sequence ID is reset when the recorder process is restarted.
        httpRequest - the data about a HTTP request.
